      <title>Rio Tinto废料计划筹集高达50亿美元的股票销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/rio-tinto-scraps-plans-to-raise-up-to-5-billion-in-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士说，在投资者的推动下，里约热内卢集团（Rio Tinto Group）取消了计划，以筹集多达50亿美元的股份出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/rio-tinto-scraps-plans-to-raise-up-to-5-billion-in-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 18:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
